metadata.name: GEOMETRIC #37
metadata.description:
Following the search for formal simplification, where everything is built using simple geometric figures, aggregations to planes and colors, lights and shadows.

Features:
PALLETS
In total, the work has 31 different color palettes, with probability percentages ranging from 2% to 7%.

FORMS
The images are structured using just four simple shapes (square, rectangle, circle and triangle) proportional to each other.

The use of each of the forms follows six different combination patterns.

VECTOR
Rectangular elements can have two orientations (horizontal or vertical).

SATURATION
In total, four levels of color saturation are applied, ranging from 25% to 100%.

CANVAS
Altogether there are four different canvas formats, in the following proportions: 1x2, 2x3, 3x4 and 1x1.

FRAGMENTATION AND DENSITY
Finally, the elements are combined from four stages of fragmentation and five levels of density.

November 14, 2022.

Paivei's generative token made with p5js, in celebration of the first anniversary of FxHash.

 #fxhashturnsone

metadata.name: PixelShifter #9
metadata.description:
Two simple geometric shapes repeated and slowly oscillating. 
Produced to celebrate a year of FXHash. 
Congratulations to the team and thanks to everyone who has supported me.
50% of Primary and secondary will go the the Processing foundation.

Features include 6 types of shape
Black or white background and 15 varying palettes

metadata.name: Hexagones Landscape #287
metadata.description:
An undulating (sometimes) landscape made up of hexagons (or "Hexagones" laying in wait) to celebrate the first birthday of fxhash. Written at the last minute the weekend before the birthday week.

A simpler 16 colour version of this project was originally coded on an Atari ST 512, about 32 years ago, figured it was time to update it.

INSTRUCTIONS ::

h - Toggle high-res
s - Download and save image

PRINTING INSTRUCTIONS ::

High-res will output a 6,553 x 8,192 image, at 300dpi it should print at...

21.84 x 27.3 inches
55.47 x 69.3 cm
